Package org.monarchinitiative.lirical.core.model

Class ClinVarAlleleData

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.lirical.core.model.ClinVarAlleleData
public class ClinVarAlleleData extends Object
A subset of ClinVar allele data relevant for LIRICAL analysis.

We use the primary interpretation for prioritization and the allele ID for linking out (e.g. here for an allele ID 270003)
